      <title>日本投资者称重温暖的共鸣，美国关系中的不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/japanese-investors-relieved-by-warm-vibes-from-ishiba-and-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总理西格鲁·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的会面后，周五遍布日本市场的紧张情绪短暂地救济，然后在美国总统对钢铁和铝的进口征收关税之后，在周一重新恢复了不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/japanese-investors-relieved-by-warm-vibes-from-ishiba-and-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风险悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/markets-in-eastern-europe-enjoyed-a-trump-bump-now-come-the-trade-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利的维克多·奥班（Viktor Orban）被总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）称赞为“坚强”和“聪明”，是东欧领导人之一，希望对美国的效忠将转化为交易和经济增长。取而代之的是，他们可能发现自己的金融市场无法摆脱美国欧洲贸易战的更广泛的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/markets-in-eastern-europe-enjoyed-a-trump-bump-now-come-the-trade-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
